<Description>
    <Header>
        <h5>Grouped Bar</h5>
    </Header>
    <Content>
        <p>A grouped Bar Chart places bars next to each other for each category, making it easy to compare multiple series values directly without stacking. You can group series by using the <code>GroupName</code> property in <code>ChartSeries</code>.</p>
    </Content>
</Description>
